# Design System Rules

## Colors
- Base: Zinc (neutral gray)
- Primary accent: TRAC Blue (#0c0563 based, oklch 275 hue)
- Dark mode background: oklch(0.141 0.005 285.82) - neutral dark gray
- Light mode background: oklch(1 0 0)
- TRAC blue used only for: buttons, links, highlights
- Always use CSS variables, never hardcode colors

## Spacing
- Use 4px grid system (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64)
- Tailwind: space-1 = 4px, space-2 = 8px...

## Typography
- Font: Rajdhani (local)
- Weights: 300 (Light), 400 (Regular), 500 (Medium), 600 (SemiBold), 700 (Bold)
- Fallback: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif
- Sizes: text-sm, text-base, text-lg, text-xl, text-2xl
- Headings: font-semibold (600) or font-bold (700)
- Body: font-normal (400) or font-medium (500)

## Border Radius
- Small elements: rounded-md (6px)
- Cards/containers: rounded-lg (8px)
- Pills/badges: rounded-full

## Shadows
- Minimal shadows, prefer border definition
- Dark mode: no shadows, use border-border